# Borg Memory — {{ namespace }}

This project uses Borg ({{ borg_url }}) for persistent AI memory across sessions.

## Usage

- **Namespace:** Always use `{{ namespace }}` in all Borg tool calls.
- **borg_think:** Call before complex tasks (debugging, architecture decisions, unfamiliar code).
- **borg_learn:** Call after significant decisions or non-obvious fixes.
- **borg_recall:** Call for direct memory searches when you need raw results.

## Rules

- Do NOT learn secrets, API keys, passwords, tokens, or PII.
- Do NOT learn routine changes obvious from git history.
- Do NOT omit the namespace parameter.
